name: TWIRLY SKIRT SETS
description:
Your princess will LOVE the fullness of this TWIRLY skirt!

~Professionally sewn skirt is made with two complementary fabrics and has an elastic waist for a comfortable fit.
~The flirty shirt has ruffles on the sleeves and hemline and features a machine-embroidered, appliqued flower using the same fabric as the skirt.
~Our handmade hairbow tops off this feminine ensemble.

Machine washable. Light iron if desired on skirt.

See the pictures of all designs in our Facebook "Twirly Skirt Sets" album. Size 3/4 Flower Power is shown here.

name: TUTU BAGS
description:
You WILL get noticed carrying one of our Tutu Bags!!

~Large bag is 13" x 13".
~Medium bag is 11" x 8.5". 
~Small bag is 6" x 6".

Sturdy canvas bag is embellished with its own "tutu" skirt and ribbon.

Hand-wash and hang to dry.

See pictures of all designs in our Facebook "Tutu Bags" album. Large bag in Leopard design is shown here. 

Custom designs available. Name can be machine-embroidered for additional $12.

name: AMERICAN GIRL DOLL FANCY TUTU SETS
description:
Christmas is coming!!! 

Your little girl will be charmed by our Jingle Elf (shown here) tutu set for her American Girl Doll (or an 18" inch doll with similar proportions).

Handmade tutu....complete with jingle bells!
Professionally, machine embroidered shirt which snaps in back.
Two of our special pony tutus for the doll's hair.

Machine wash shirt.
Handwash tutu and pony tutus.

See the pictures in our Facebook "American Girl Doll ~ Fancy Tutu Sets" album. Our doll sets are made to match the Fancy Tutu Sets we make for infants through girls which you can see in the two "Fancy Tutu Sets" albums on our Facebook page.

name: FANCY TUTU SETS
description:
Your little dancer will NEVER want to take this tutu set off! Tutu Set shown is a Toddler size in our DANCE design.

Beautiful handmade, double-layer tutu embellished with ribbons.
Professionally machine embroidered with ballet shoes -- our shirt is very feminine.
Gorgeous hairbow made with matching ribbon.

See the pictures in our TWO Facebook albums "FANCY TUTU SETS".

Shirt is machine washable.
Tutu skirt should be hand-washed and hung to dry.
Hairbow can be ordered with alligator clip, or small to large barrette.
